## Best Practices

### Executive Summary
- **Good**: "Workday is uniquely positioned to develop the AI-Powered Interview Team Optimization Skill for the 2026R1+ release. This intelligent skill will proactively recommend an optimal interview team to a hiring manager, the moment a job requisition is created, leveraging our comprehensive talent data."
- **Bad**: "This PRD describes a new feature for interviews."

### Strategic Value & Outcomes
- **Good**: "Reduce Time to Fill: This feature aims to reduce the Time to First Interview Team Creation from its current baseline of 16.6 days."
- **Bad**: "Will help with time to fill."

### Feature Solution
- **Good**: Bullet list format
  - "• Hiring Manager conversationally invokes the Skill via Workday Chat"
  - "• Skill intelligently suggests an interview team"
- **Bad**: Long prose paragraphs describing the feature

### Year 1 Forecast
- **Good**: "Adoption Target: 4.5% | Usage Volume: ~750,000 recommendations | Basis: This forecast applies a 4.5% adoption rate, aligning with the observed Year 1 uptake of the first AI feature..."
- **Bad**: "We expect good adoption"

